detailedRequirements:
-----------------This is a community event and therefore a non-paid challenge-----------------

Calling all topcoder members!

What better way to show off a community than creating a portrait that involves their participation.  This is where I need all of YOU!  Starting today you can submit to this challenge with a photo of yourself.  In about a month's time we will aggregate all of your images and create a mosaic of the topcoder logo!

If you are not sure what a mosaic is, take a look at this picture of Woody from Toy Story made up of different images.

This is the master logo that we will be creating:  

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

We will need images of all sorts of colors to fill in the image so please keep that in mind!  The image is predominately white, it has black lettering, with the logo being a mix of orange, yellow, green, and blue

We will keep this open for a month or until we reach 10,000 photos.  So get creative with your photo submission and I cannot wait to see how this mosaic turns out!

Let's get to it, topcoder!
finalSubmissionGuidelines: Submit a jpg or png of yourself to this challenge with the filename in the format of <topcoder username>.jpg
